{"tid":112650,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"★[2017 Feb 8] iOS10.2.1新Bug：同時按下這兩個鍵可導致死機！","createTime":"2017-02-08T09:51:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T10:03:44.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d28aaf46e4f4102ec670dc9ce653220969a54cc5","tid":112650,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:51:30.000Z","msg":"只要在控制中心，時按下AirDrop與Camera鍵，就會造成手機死機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2017/2/20170208_172845_742.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ithome.com%2Fnewsuploadfiles%2F2017%2F2%2F20170208_172845_742.jpg&h=521f5fb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource:(含蝗文)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ithome.com/html/iphone/292430.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com%2Fhtml%2Fiphone%2F292430.htm&d=tLsEO8KpRnvfRHW%2FlT3Tjm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=75bd3c7d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ithome.com/html/iphone/292430.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1ced80ee84391e85b0bd86707868a5dd979362eb","tid":112650,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:52:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc3b5e79c1d73c5598362ab8694902777a7e1c2c","tid":112650,"uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T10:17:09.000Z","msg":"睇過？<br />\n冇事喎<br />\niPhone 6s<br />\nIphone7"},{"pid":"9da32247b918d54d0dec335ad5bb33e969ac3ca1","tid":112650,"uid":74947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T10:38:06.000Z","msg":"iPhone7plus 真係卡死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要power+volume down reboot"},{"pid":"1a96e163f90adb55249c96d195564bc49177cb4a","tid":112650,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T10:38:08.000Z","msg":"之前一段時間，網上有不少讓iPhone痛不欲生的BUG，這完全打破蘋果之前宣稱的新版iOS系統十分安全的說法，比如著名的彩虹短信攻擊，那各位是不是認為除此之外就沒有別的漏洞了呢？<br />\n　　小伙子別天真了，那只是沒人研究而已，這不，又有大神發現了iOS系統的最新BUG，而且iOS10.2.1也不例外哦，雖然不是很嚴重的漏洞，但足以讓你的手機一旦這麼操作了就能立即死機，黑屏並重新載入畫面。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.elecfans.com/3g/news/20170205479810.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.elecfans.com%2F3g%2Fnews%2F20170205479810.html&d=tLsEO8KpRnvfRHW%2FlT3Tjm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=72436e2d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.elecfans.com/3g/news/20170205479810.html</a><br />\n<br />\nBUG一：<br />\n<br />\n首先我們在iPhone主界面底部向上滑動呼出控制中心<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.elecfans.com/uploads/allimg/170205/09363TQ8-0.jpg?id=0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.elecfans.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F170205%2F09363TQ8-0.jpg%3Fid%3D0&h=5d1f5d47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f382e82cfc2f2639d628dc2a8e212b248ee0625d","tid":112650,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T10:38:59.000Z","msg":"接下來的操作也沒什麼難度，我們只要同時按下紅框1和紅框2中的按鈕，你的iPhone就會立刻死機，黑屏，並重新載入主畫面，記住一定要同時按下才有效。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.elecfans.com/uploads/allimg/170205/09363UV1-1.jpg?id=0&amp;width=720\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.elecfans.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F170205%2F09363UV1-1.jpg%3Fid%3D0%26width%3D720&h=ae1d926b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3baa5925819f73666d47902e7b44dd612d43968","tid":112650,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T10:41:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">BUG二：</span><br />\n<br />\n接下來這個BUG引起的效果和上面的一樣，不同的是不再需要解鎖進入到主畫面，在鎖屏界面就可以完成。<br />\n　　首先在鎖屏狀態下向右滑動呼出拍攝畫面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.elecfans.com/uploads/allimg/170205/09363RP7-2.jpg?id=0&amp;width=720\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.elecfans.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F170205%2F09363RP7-2.jpg%3Fid%3D0%26width%3D720&h=5e285cc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後再向上滑動呼出控制中心，並點擊計算機按鈕進入計算頁面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.elecfans.com/uploads/allimg/170205/09363Wa7-3.jpg?id=0&amp;width=720\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.elecfans.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F170205%2F09363Wa7-3.jpg%3Fid%3D0%26width%3D720&h=080c8b49&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ee5be33cf667cd59e5a1bbd2d5499b919171e2d","tid":112650,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T10:41:56.000Z","msg":"這時我們長按電源鍵直到出現手機重啟頁面，只要點擊底部的叉叉，iPhone就會立刻黑屏，並載入主界面。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.elecfans.com/uploads/allimg/170205/09363T456-4.jpg?id=0&amp;width=720\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.elecfans.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F170205%2F09363T456-4.jpg%3Fid%3D0%26width%3D720&h=a3e9d4bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37effcb0bff2979d3266663ddd4527c319ced12b","tid":112650,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T10:42:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>iPhone7plus 真係卡死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要power+volume down reboot</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e52e74998a0f8646448848bcfd083197baf0e9e9","tid":112650,"uid":1723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T10:49:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/08/184901_e402f41076b6603597fcc08d0528a8a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F08%2F184901_e402f41076b6603597fcc08d0528a8a5.jpg&h=b90956ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b63491af1ff227891ac5dd278c098b3e314aef","tid":112650,"uid":1723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T10:50:50.000Z","msg":"第二個的確有，但唔係死機"},{"pid":"5f6e972a5b78a39c56dc52144d93a62153a305b0","tid"